org.dockbox.selene.core.objects.keys

Class RemovableKey<K,A>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dockbox.selene.core.objects.keys.Key<K,A>
      • org.dockbox.selene.core.objects.keys.RemovableKey<K,A>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - The type parameter indicating the constraint for the type to apply to/retrieve from.
    A - The type parameter indicating the constraint for the value to be applied/retrieved.

    public abstract class RemovableKey<K,A>
extends Key<K,A>
    A low-level type which can be used in combination with a KeyHolder to dynamically apply, retrieve, and remove values from types. The apply and retrieve functionality is inherited and unchanged from Key.
